    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "On April 26, 1967, [REDACTED] at the Miami Office and",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "furnished the following information relating to an object,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "presently referred to as an unidentified flying object, he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "allegedly photographed during November, 1944:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Sometime during 1943, he graduated from the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "German Air Academy and was assigned as a member of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Luftwaffe on the Russian Front. Near the end of 1944, he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "was released from this duty and was assigned as a test",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "pilot to a top secret project in the Black Forest of Austria.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "During this period he observed the aircraft described above.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "It was saucer shaped, about twenty-one feet in diameter,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "radio controlled, and mounted several jet engines around the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "exterior portion of the craft. He further described the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "exterior portion as revolving around the dome in the center",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "which remained stationary. It was [REDACTED] responsibility",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "to photograph the object while in flight. He asserted he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "was able to retain a negative of a photograph he made at 7,000",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "meters (20,000 feet). A Xerox copy of the negative, as furnished",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "by [REDACTED], appears on the last page of this communication.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Also, a still photograph he allegedly made \"at the risk of my",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "life\", illustrating the object parked in a hanger, appears on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "the last page.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "According to [REDACTED] the above aircraft was designed",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "and engineered by (First Name Unknown) [REDACTED] a German engineer",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "whose present whereabouts is unknown to him. He assumed [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "was taken into custody by Allied Forces upon the termination",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "of hostilities. [REDACTED] stated [REDACTED] unsuccessfully attempted",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "to avoid the German draft, but was apprehended by the Gestapo",
